{"tid":887883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國民黨:禁止政治抗議, 把馬路還給民眾","createTime":"2018-11-03T09:30:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T07:29:00.000Z","uid":134071,"like":7,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"2ab7f61d8a44b6ce9ff031b54794d8d0ff608aa9","tid":887883,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T09:30:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://tw.news.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20181101/1458404/?fbclid=IwAR2jbnNZCnERUs7tDXm8LVeM-q4FQBL9RMjE-dUU149nUmz-aqEFI5odZ9w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2Frealtime%2F20181101%2F1458404%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2jbnNZCnERUs7tDXm8LVeM-q4FQBL9RMjE-dUU149nUmz-aqEFI5odZ9w&d=lEbLpYQusR8VjQlStmRorp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=57b2df7c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2Frealtime%2F20181101%2F1458404%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2jbnNZCnERUs7tDXm8LVeM-q4FQBL9RMjE-dUU149nUmz-aqEFI5odZ9w&h=aa0b557c\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.news.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20181101/1458404/?fbclid=IwAR2jbnNZCnERUs7tDXm8LVeM-q4FQBL9RMjE-dUU149nUmz-aqEFI5odZ9w</a></span><br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜當選後禁政治抗議　丁守中贊同：大家一起拚經濟<br />\n出版時間：2018/11/01 13:39<br />\n<br />\n<strong>國民黨高雄市長候選人韓國瑜日前指出，高雄20多年來被意識型態纏的喘不過氣來，未來當選高雄市長後，政治的抗議，意識型態的請願都不准，要專心拚經濟</strong>，但言論遭批違憲後，韓則改口稱市長再怎麼厲害，也不能超越《憲法》。<strong>國民黨台北市長丁守中今受訪贊同韓國瑜說法，丁表示，韓國瑜講的完全正確，大家要一起拚台北與台灣的經濟。</strong><br />\n <br />\n丁守中表示，像是台北市長柯文哲要搞政治，騙藍騙綠遊走在各種政治訴求之間，態度反覆，台北應該要作為台灣整體的火車頭，也要做為南部農產的運銷中心，將來也會跟韓國瑜等中南部縣市長一起拚經濟。<br />\n <br />\n韓國瑜也說要政治抗議就到台北去，丁守中則說，韓國瑜說的沒錯，就讓柯文哲來搞政治，柯天天在操作、算計藍綠。<br />\n <br />\n<strong>至於韓國瑜的訴求是否違法違憲？丁守中則說，要把馬路還給民眾，太多政治抗爭對經濟發展、社會穩定沒有幫助</strong>，太多意識形態與台獨訴求對台灣沒有幫助，兩岸關係要好，台灣的經濟才會更好，因為中國是台灣最大的投資市場與貿易順差來源，也是最多台商投資的地方，台灣沒有必要扛起全世界反中國的大旗，夾在西方國家與中國冷戰夾縫中，那樣對台灣經濟最不利。（戴祺修／台北報導）"},{"pid":"fc354b2c7e77c59ff4d2f2a25493e738400d4544","tid":887883,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T03:43:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed83969da459b213bc6c6898364ba4b0a8bd89c1","tid":887883,"uid":46527,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T03:45:54.000Z","msg":"國民黨一早變哂共產黨"},{"pid":"25372079c6c62c6452ca968b3a5fa8ee2544d779","tid":887883,"uid":35790,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T03:52:31.000Z","msg":"越來越似香港建制口吻<br />\n攪好經濟民生 少攪政治爭拗"},{"pid":"388951e9bec74873048f89ac367295b842728238","tid":887883,"uid":8071,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T03:57:28.000Z","msg":"柯文哲要搞政治 &lt;- 有冇搞L錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408977df4da3150c754db6125622d45919813bef","tid":887883,"uid":35790,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T04:06:02.000Z","msg":"國民黨總理 孫中山：政治就係眾人之事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cd5bb3b479069cb7f82222152be1e2fa96781a4","tid":887883,"uid":479,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T04:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/05/122019_e5a98c8e26ca791ad6e0769e2966509b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F05%2F122019_e5a98c8e26ca791ad6e0769e2966509b.png&h=e248f78c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搞政治果個仲可以減成千億元債務<br />\n佢都好能者多勞下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d86a62320bdfce3733c21168b8a4017ee32fb7b","tid":887883,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T04:29:26.000Z","msg":"韓國瑜 咩人黎?"},{"pid":"f984d194a6a19d1e75814475fd2cccd841b57346","tid":887883,"uid":144372,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2cd5bb3b479069cb7f82222152be1e2fa96781a4","tid":887883,"uid":479,"like":52,"dislike":0,"score":52,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T04:21:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://im